block intro
	.page-intro: .container
		h1 About
		p We are standing up for our rights as Oklahomans. We stand proud for the legalization of marijuana to improve the health and well-being of the people of Oklahoma and eliminate the terrors of the War on Marijuana.
		p From out of a network of grassroots organizations scattered through-out the state, LegalizeOK is actively working on ending cannabis prohibition in Oklahoma by means of the ballot initiative process.

